    "project_template_level_name": "CSA U7L3-L1 Overloaded PBT_alt-2025",
    "teacher_markdown": "Students should notice that the `MusicPlayer` uses the `play()` method that matches the argument that the method is called with. So when the `play()` method is called with a `Song` object, the method with the `Song` parameter is called.",
